title: Tesla Is Accused of Tolerating Racial Harassment, in EEOC Suit
description: Equal Employment Opportunity Commission sues Elon Musk’s EV company, alleging Black employees were subjected to a hostile work environment.

title: Nvidia's French Offices Raided in Competition Inquiry
description: France’s competition authority, which carried out the raid, has expressed concerns that cloud-computing companies could exclude smaller competitors.

title: In Suing Amazon, FTC's Lina Khan Turns Her Earlier Pricing Argument on Its Head
description: The government’s antitrust lawsuit is a more streamlined complaint that leaves out some allegations from the FTC chair’s famous law-school paper.

title: Secrecy of Google Antitrust Trial Leads to Blame Game
description: The judge and government lawyers are defending themselves against criticism for letting tech executives testify behind closed doors.

title: X CEO Linda Yaccarino Says Platform Should Turn Profit in 2024
description: The former ad executive emphasized X’s transformation from previous incarnation as Twitter, focusing on broader vision over specific user metrics.

title: iPhone 15 Pro Owners Complain About Overheating Problems
description: The issue threatens Apple’s premium phones, a cash cow essential to its growth and profits.
